<section id="benefits" class="benefits" href="#benefits">
  <div class="hydrophobics" id="hydrophobics"><img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/128/2792/2792706.png" width="110" alt="water droplets">
  </div>
  <div class="hydrophobics-text">
    <h2>Hydrophobic Properties</h2>
    <p>Ceramic coatings provide exceptional hydrophobic benefits by creating a durable, nano-ceramic layer on the vehicle's surface that repels water, dirt, and contaminants. This layer minimizes water spots and helps prevent grime from adhering, making cleaning significantly easier. </p>
  </div>
  <div class="superior-protection" id="superior-protection"><img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/128/2100/2100165.png" width="110" alt="uv ray protection icon">
  </div>
  <div class="superior-protection-text">
    <h2>Superior Protection</h2>
    <p>They protect against harmful elements like bird droppings, acid rain, UV rays, and road salts, which can damage paint. </p>
  </div>
   <div class="enhanced-appearance" id="enhanced-appearance"><img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/128/3808/3808030.png" width="110" alt="shiny car icon">
  </div>
  <div class="enhanced-appearance-text">
    <h2>Enhanced Appearance</h2>
    <p>Ceramic coatings enhance a vehicle's appearance by adding a deep, glossy finish and preserving the paint's color and vibrancy over time.</p>
  </div>
